query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS workflow_events (
  id VARCHAR(32) PRIMARY KEY,
  workflow_id VARCHAR(32) NOT NULL,
  type ENUM('prompt_llm', 'llm_response', 'tool_call', 'tool_result', 'memory_load', 'memory_save', 'w_matrix_transform', 'package_upload', 'package_validate', 'package_process', 'package_complete', 'error', 'user_input', 'system_event') NOT NULL,
  status ENUM('pending', 'running', 'completed', 'failed') NOT NULL,
  title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  description TEXT,
  timestamp BIGINT NOT NULL,
  duration INT,
  input JSON,
  output JSON,
  metadata JSON,
  error JSON,
  parent_event_id VARCHAR(32),
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX workflow_idx (workflow_id),
  INDEX type_idx (type),
  INDEX status_idx (status),
  INDEX timestamp_idx (timestamp),
  INDEX parent_idx (parent_event_id)
)
